text: Tayeb Braikia (born 8 March 1974 in Århus) is a Danish former cyclist. ==Major results== ;1996 :1st 20px U23 National Road Race Championships ;1997 :1st Stages 1 & 5 Cinturón a Mallorca :2nd Midtbank Grand Prix :3rd Overall Tour de Berlin ;1998 :1st Ronde van Overijssel ;1999 :1st Overall Circuit Franco-Belge ::1st Stages 1 & 4 ;2001 :1st Clásica de Almería ==References== Category:1974 births Category:Living people Category:Danish male cyclists Category:Giro d'Italia cyclists Category:Sportspeople from Aarhus
title: Tayeb Braikia
